been part of prestigious leagues in countries like Italy or Spain. But
that is not enough to ensure good teamwork."
</P>
<P>
He added, "Croatia's strength is in individual players. If we can
manage to take advantage of their mistakes we'll have a good chance of
winning." 
</P>
