He announced the breakthrough after a meeting of Cambodian and
Vietnamese chief representatives of the conclusion of the first
round bilateral border talks.
</P>
<P>
He said the three-day talks between Cambodia and Vietnam ended
on Friday after reaching common views on some important issues in
principle.
</P>
<P>
Talks over contentious land and sea border issues were a result
of a meeting between Cambodia's First Prime Minister Ung Huot and
his Vietnamese counterpart Phan Van Khai earlier this month in
Hanoi.
</P>
