here on Friday that the new Tricolore ball should not be blamed for
some of goals scored during the World Cup finals.
</P>
<P>
"The new ball is not the reason for the goals sometimes blamed on
the goalkeepers," said the keeper who plays for the French club
Olympique Marseille.
</P>
