<HEADLINE> 2 Lebanese Die in Car Explosion </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIRUT, June 19 (Xinhua) -- Two Lebanese were killed in a car
blast here early Friday morning, the National Broadcast Network
radio reported.
</P>
<P>
